WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.200
The operator reviews the order awaiting processing.

00:08.200 --> 00:12.500
The same order reaches a failed state with a recovery action available.

00:12.500 --> 00:16.200
The normal scenario is restored and retry processing is requested.

00:16.200 --> 00:23.100
The same order is processed again and reaches recovered status.

00:23.100 --> 00:23.467
Recovery is complete.
